title: '"I learned that in order to feel fully witnessed and understood, some parts need to take over in the body temporarily. Now whenever I see signs, even subtle signs, of a somatic takeover, I encourage clients to stay with or even exaggerate that experience. If some of their other parts feel self-conscious or frightened, we stop first to help them feel safe so they are willing to step back and let us proceed."'
pid: 9123887e-92cc-4ebc-a03a-a3572a1264f2
